      <description>
        &lt;p&gt;
Some translations are currently done with full locales (i.e. pt_BR) but we don't also have pt_PT and so where I would normally default to the language if there are only one translation I am unsure what to do in this case.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
Currently supports the short language code or the locale code, but this will need to be resolved before we address &lt;a class="closed ticket" href="http://localhost/ticket/1653" title="enhancement: Change URLs for multilingual site (closed: fixed)"&gt;#1653&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
